Mail-Send-Loop version 0.1
==========================

Standard Pure Perl SMTP Module.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  IO::Socket
  MIME::Lite

